      "rationale": "The pedicle screw material (Ti-6Al-4V) is represented by a bilinear isotropic hardening model calibrated to ASTM E8 tensile coupon data. Frictional contact at the screw-rod interface uses a penalty formulation with coefficient of friction 0.2, consistent with published tribological data for titanium-on-titanium interfaces under physiological loading."
