      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and ultimate strength were measured from coupons machined from the same Ti-6Al-4V bar stock as the test constructs. CMM measurements of screw geometry were incorporated directly into the CAD model. A 1000-sample Monte Carlo propagation confirmed that input uncertainty contributes less than 3% to total QoI uncertainty."
