      "rationale": "Eleven constructs were assembled from a single production lot of non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws. All components underwent incoming dimensional inspection per DePuy Synthes QMS. Coefficient of variation in measured stiffness across the 11 specimens was 4.2%, indicating acceptable inter-specimen variability."
