      "rationale": "Testing was performed at a single 40 mm anterior offset per ASTM F1717. While this replicates the standard regulatory condition, it does not span the full range of clinical loading configurations. This factor is assessed below the required level; the shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given that the COU is explicitly limited to the F1717 standard test condition."
