      "rationale": "For all three QoIs, the validation metric E/uval was below 1.96 (stiffness: 1.31, yield force: 1.54, force at 40 mm: 1.18). Percent differences between ensemble-mean FEA and experimental mean were 4.7%, 6.1%, and 3.9% respectively, all within the pre-established 10% acceptance bound."
